120678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeebd0212014995f16840a87e10904804aed7111","tid":1875364,"uid":160758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdd2e33e105be0f9c77e66d0d24f53e1982002e0","tid":1875364,"uid":349074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a10136a26783acf0d9ee42e1a328bee0de7464","tid":1875364,"uid":234718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"其實translation同linguistics好多畢業都唔係做番本行，香港做翻譯唔值錢<br />\nlinguistics如果有興趣讀落去，可以讀埋master，讀speech therapy，將來做言語治療師"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:06:53.000Z","msg":"言語治療師係香港吃唔吃香"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:25:38.000Z","msg":"吃香，但係你要讀言語治療instead of 語言學。同埋讀speech therapy想做言語治療師一定要讀master，言語治療其實同語言學關係唔大。<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果想翻釋同語言學二揀一嘅話，興趣緊要啲，因為兩者出路都唔係太特別。翻釋係專業，但係翻咩先係重點，要睇你本身能力（翻文學好難，翻商業嘢嘅話其實個個都識中英文，唔專精某行業嘅翻譯應該會最後同讀語言學差唔多出路）；語言學其實出路百搭，但係本質係乞食科，要睇下自己係咪真係有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n你想繼續讀書(master/mphil/phd)嘅話，linguistics通常唔係單純linguistics，會溝埋其他科(psycho, bio, anthro, etc.)，所以都要睇你鐘意咩。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 想讀ling嘅話不如學多隻語言，interview會好有用。<br />\nP.P.S.最緊要興趣:p"},{"pid":"225227d1f4f021562c846456115fd6566c16c490","tid":1875364,"uid":314808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"絲打 我同你同科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fb5f6a6ea32656e88e7d450e33fae502d12af8","tid":1875364,"uid":349074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"225227d1f4f021562c846456115fd6566c16c490","tid":1875364,"uid":314808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"絲打 我同你同科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:35:03.000Z","msg":"冇tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}